data.rationale:
This a plugin for Template, thus the Template::Plugin prefix (a
    standard for Template plugins). It's an interface for
    Data::HTMLDumper, thus the Data::HTMLDumper portion of the
    namespace.

    This module is much like Template::Plugin::Dumper, but displays the
    results formatted in an HTML table, as opposed to
    Template::Plugin::Dumper's raw output.
